title: Beatwin
text:
Beatwin (Korean: 비트윈; pronounced Between; stylized as BEATWIN) was a South Korean boy band formed by Elen Entertainment (formerly Heavenly Star Content) in Seoul, South Korea. The group currently consists of two members: Sunhyeok and Youngho. They debuted on January 6, 2014 with the single "She's My Girl". Their fans are called "Trophy".
